    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，所以这是一个支付链路的时间轴。T0ms作为起点，用户提交表单。我想确认一下，Payment service接收请求是在T10ms吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T0ms",
        "T10ms",
        "Payment service"
