      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，T10ms。然后这里有个关键细节——在Payment service内部，IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode要处理两个并行检查：5ms的幂等性校验和8ms的JWT验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T10ms",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "idempotency check",
        "JWT validation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把这两个检查作为T10ms下的子项列出来。接下来到T25ms应该是钱包余额检查了吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "T25ms",
